          "reviewBody": "Poor infrastructure and very unsystematic management. They have taken around one and half month to just set the time table of the classes. Teacher Student ration is 1:45.\nMost of the rowdy marathi crowd is here to study or not study I can say. Children and management have zero respect for teachers. Recently they did the palki and waari celebration, I saw most of the staff only taking pictures. Nothing was explained to students why we celebrate the yatra, history around it. Very pathetic experience.",
