            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "This is one of best schools in Pune.The staff is really helpful and friendly.My son is studying there.I would specially like to thank Bhavana Ma'am and the teachers for efficiently handling the covid situation by ensuring that the students progress isn't compromised and being mindful of any problem a student a may face during online classes. The teachers are knowledgeable as well as they're empathetic to the students' issues. I got a chance to interact with Mankar ma'am and Aditya sir and I was impressed that  they know what my son is good at as well as areas of improvements(personal attention).",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
