          },
          "reviewBody": "One of the best schools in Balewadi area with the best teachers. The teachers plan their subject in advance to make sure it is interactive session. Kudos for all the hardworking the teachers, staff and Principal have put up during this pandemic ensuring no loss of study to the students.\nGreat place and great vision by the school management and leadership team",
          "publisher": {
